name: Taco Collector 3D
description:
oh no!

you accidentally spilled your tacos in the haunted mansion of time travel, meaning that you might accidentally create an alternate timeline, putting your existence in jeopardy! quickly, pick up the tacos before the dinosaurs discover tacos too early, or the ghost gaurdians of time catch you and force you out! 

my first shot at a 3D game, made in scratch
